@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<style>
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
        color: white;
    }
    #mainContainer {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 40px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .header h1 {
        color: #4e54c8;
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
    #lead {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffbb00, #4851ff);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        animation: gradient 3s infinite;
        background-size: 200% 200%;
    }
    @@keyframes gradient {
        0% {
            background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
            background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
        100% {
            background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
    }
    .content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .content img {
        max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .content p {
        color: #333;
        text-align: justify;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #4e54c8;
        border-color: #4e54c8;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #8f94fb;
        border-color: #8f94fb;
    }
    .parallax {
        background-attachment: fixed;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        min-height: 400px;
        width: 100%;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .parallax-content {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>

<div class="container" id="mainContainer">
    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Student Portal App</h1>
        <p class="lead" id="lead">Your one-stop solution for managing student information efficiently and effectively.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="parallax" style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184298/pexels-photo-3184298.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940');"></div>
        <div class="parallax-content">
            <p>The Student Portal App is designed to provide students with a comprehensive platform to manage their academic information. This project is built using ASP.NET Core, a powerful framework for building web applications. The app allows students to view and update their personal information, track their academic progress, and communicate with their instructors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="parallax" style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184631/pexels-photo-3184631.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940');"></div>
        <div class="parallax-content">
            <p>Our goal is to create an intuitive and user-friendly interface that makes it easy for students to access the information they need. The app includes features such as course registration, grade tracking, and a messaging system to facilitate communication between students and faculty.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="parallax" style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184328/pexels-photo-3184328.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940');"></div>
        <div class="parallax-content">
            <p>We are committed to continuously improving the Student Portal App by incorporating feedback from users and staying up-to-date with the latest advancements in web development. Join us on this journey to enhance the educational experience for students everywhere.</p>
            <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


